programme.title: Kirstie and Phil's Love It or List It
programme.desc: Kirstie Allsopp heads back to Albrighton in Shropshire to catch up with Jamie Lea and Curtis, a couple whose Love It or List It journey began in 2019 with their three-bed terrace house that was a full-blown battleground. Jamie Lea dreamed of putting down roots, focusing on family life with daughter Scarlett and preparing for baby number two but Curtis had other ideas. Ever restless, he was glued to property sites, hunting for their next fixer-upper: a bigger home with a sprawling countryside garden for their growing family. Kirstie swooped in with a daring 30,000 Love It plan, and the couple rolled up their sleeves, stretching every penny with a mix of DIY grit and determination. Meanwhile, armed with a 280,000 List It budget, Phil uncovered some jaw-dropping homes - including a dreamy four-bed project - that left them seriously torn. Then, in 2023, Phil revisited and found the couple stuck in selling limbo. Never one to shy away from tough love, he dished out pearls of wisdom to help get them back on track. Now, Kirstie uncovers the next chapter in Jamie Lea and Curtis's roller coaster story. programme.title: Seeking Satoshi: The Mystery Bitcoin Creator

Now a multi trillion-dollar industry, its pseudonymous inventor has not been heard from since 2011. Whoever it is could be one of the richest people on the planet, and yet their identity remains unknown. Whilst on the trail for Bitcoin's inventor, Gabriel uncovers a conspiracy to end democracy and transform the world as we know it

programme.title: Super Surgeons: A Chance at Life

programme.title: Dispatches
programme.desc: Reporter Ellie Flynn investigates Britain's obsession with weight loss injections and asks whether profits are being prioritised over patient safety. Undercover filming exposes the drugs being sold by a major high street chain to an under-age patient; and exposes registered NHS nurses prescribing the jabs without proper checks on patients. With an estimated half a million Britons currently being prescribed weight loss drugs, Ellie talks to experts who are concerned about the lack of oversight, asking why there are so many obese patients who are unable to get these drugs on the NHS, and reveals for the first time entire areas of the country where the NHS is not prescribing the medication

Chloe has emetophobia - the phobia of people being sick - and talks about her sadness at not being able to care for her three young daughters. Chloe's eldest daughter is already starting to show signs of the same phobia, after seeing Chloe's reaction. Milly's had a phobia of frogs for as long as she remembers. programme.desc: Las cmicas espaolas ms caeras tomarn las riendas del canal con el especial Roast Battle: Pelea como una mujer, compuesto por las mejores batallas donde todo est permitido .

programme.title: La que se avecina - T8, E01: Un hombre salvaje, una vieja maldita y un fanta...
programme.desc: La convivencia de la comunidad se ve alterada por la llegada al 2 C de doa Fina (Petra Martnez), una anciana problemtica, quejica, solitaria y trasnochadora que pondr en jaque a los vecinos y especialmente a Antonio y a Berta.

programme.title: La que se avecina - T8, E04: Una gastroscopia, una fiesta loca, loca y el re...
programme.desc: Los problemas econmicos de la comunidad llevan a Enrique a plantear un plan de cobro de morosos. Adems, la intencin de Edurne de vender el piso de su difunta madre activar un plan para intentar cobrar la deuda que acumula con la comunidad.

programme.title: Aqu no hay quien viva - T1, E04: rase un rumor
programme.desc: Los padres de Fernando vienen de visita y ste le pide a Alicia que se haga pasar por su novia, ya que stos no saben que es gay y no quiere darles un disgusto.

programme.title: Aqu no hay quien viva - T1, E09: rase una de miedo
programme.desc: Marisa y Vicenta le cuentan a Paco, Emilio y Jos Miguel que hace muchos aos el portero de la finca se volvi loco y prendi fuego a la casa. Paco decide grabar una pelcula de miedo con los vecinos de protagonistas pero sin que stos lo sepan.

programme.title: Torrente 5
programme.desc: Torrente sale de la crcel en el ao 2018. La Espaa que se encuentra no le gusta y decide convertirse en un 'fuera de la ley'.

programme.title: Torrente 5
programme.desc: Torrente sale de la crcel en el ao 2018. La Espaa que se encuentra no le gusta y decide convertirse en un 'fuera de la ley'.

programme.title: Malcolm - T5, E13: La hermana de Lois (Episodio n. 100)
programme.desc: Susan, la hermana de Lois, va de visita y compra caros regalos a los chicos, incluyendo un Ford Mustang descapotable; Francis y un escolta se pierden en una zona remota del rancho.

programme.title: Malcolm - T6, E08: Lois contra Jamie
programme.desc: Lois, que intenta ganarse a Jamie, hace que Francis vuelva a casa para ayudarle a recordar cmo lo conquist cuando era un nio. Entretanto, Malcolm, Reese y Dewey se comen los sesos para darle un uso divertido a un viejo trampoln.

programme.title: Malcolm - T6, E18: El baile de Ida
programme.desc: Ida obliga a Lois a preparar una tarta especial para conmemorar un santo del viejo mundo. Malcolm encuentra una asignatura que le encanta en la que no tiene que esforzarse mucho. Hal trata de intimar con Reese viendo con l pelculas de terror.

programme.title: Malcolm - T7, E16: Lois ataca de nuevo
programme.desc: Despus de que cuatro chicas humillen a Reese, Lois decide vengarse de las jvenes. Hal, escondido en el garaje, construye una mquina que lanza pelotas.

programme.title: Modern Family - T4, E01: Criando un beb
programme.desc: Llega el cumpleaos de Jay y, pese a no querer regalos ni sorpresas, Phil le lleva de pesca. Mientras, Gloria busca la mejor forma de dar la noticia sobre su embarazo.

programme.title: Modern Family - T4, E05: Visita a la casa de los horrores
programme.desc: Claire ha tenido malas experiencias con el Halloween de los ltimos aos, por lo que Phil decide hacer una jornada de puertas abiertas en su casa en la noche de Halloween.

programme.title: Modern Family - T4, E06: El rastrillo
programme.desc: Una venta de garaje familiar deja al descubierto muchos trastos viejos.

programme.title: Modern Family - T4, E12: El aguafiestas
programme.desc: Una fiesta sorpresa en verdad colma las expectativas cuando tiene lugar en la casa de los Pritchett.

programme.title: Futurama - T2, E13: Bicclope para dos
programme.desc: Leela por fin encuentra a otro miembro de su especie, un varn muy atractivo. Sin embargo, cuando resulta que es un cretino, Leela teme que, si le abandona, su especie acabar extinta.

programme.title: Futurama - T2, E19: Mi problema con los Popplers
programme.desc: Unos poderosos extraterrestres amenazan con devorar a toda la raza humana cuando la tripulacin del Planet Express importa a sus deliciosas cras como si fueran un producto gastronmico.

programme.title: Futurama - T5, E09: La picadura
programme.desc: Leela sufre graves consecuencias tras dirigir a la tripulacin en una peligrosa misin para recolectar miel de unas abejas asesinas con letales aguijones.

programme.title: Futurama - T5, E16: Las manos del diablo son juguetes ociosos
programme.desc: Fry hace un trato con el Diablo Robot para convertirse en un msico talentoso y conquistar el corazn de Leela.

programme.title: La tribu
programme.desc: Fidel, un despiadado director de Recursos Humanos, pierde su trabajo y a su familia tras un embarazoso episodio sexual con una becaria. Intentando recuperar su vida, decide hablar con su madre biolgica, que lo dio en adopcin a los 16 aos.

programme.title: La que se avecina - T8, E07: Un presidente rayado, una catarata de infortuni...
programme.desc: Brillante parodia de la vida cotidiana de cualquier comunidad de vecinos a travs de unos personajes que se relacionan con desconfianza y alimentan con su maldad intrnseca unas tramas surrealistas llenas de obsesiones personales y vecinales.

programme.title: Jubal

Western, starring Glenn Ford, Rod Steiger, Valerie French, Charles Bronson and Ernest Borgnine

programme.title: Jumanji: Welcome to the Jungle
programme.desc: Four teenagers play a jungle-themed game on an old console, only to find themselves transported into the game and transformed into its heroic characters. They must embark on a death-defying journey through the game's wilderness setting to make it back to the real world, or be stuck as video game characters forever. Fantasy action comedy, starring Dwayne Johnson, Karen Gillan, Kevin Hart and Jack Black

He goes straight to the police, but they dismiss his story as the product of an overactive imagination, forcing him to take matters into his own hands. With the help of his fiancee and secretary, he sets out to rescue the child and catch the crooks - but his only clue is the scent of a distinctive perfume. Thriller, with Van Johnson, Cecil Parker, Patricia Laffan and Vera Miles

Supernatural drama, based on a novel by Stephen King, starring Tom Hanks, Michael Clarke Duncan, David Morse and Harry Dean Stanton

programme.desc: Kirstie Allsopp and Phil Spencer look back at two shows that highlighted the need to get the balance between home and garden just right. In Bury St Edmunds, Lauren Grant believes the opportunity to build on a land she and husband Christian bought from the council will transform their confused downstairs. He, however, just wants rid of the house altogether. Meanwhile, Harrogate couple Carol and Andrew need extra space for Grandad. Can Kirstie build into their sizeable garden or will Phil find somewhere else more suitable?

programme.title: Grand Designs
programme.desc: Kevin McCloud follows a project to renovate and extend a classic 1920s cinema in Thorne, South Yorkshire. With little knowledge of restoration, Gwyn and Kate boldly set about turning the dilapidated building into a family home using masses of concrete after taking advice from an architect friend. The couple are hoping to create a hydraulic glass wall that opens up one side of the house to form a UV-filtered canopy, and there are also plans for a white roof extension that resembles a diving board

programme.title: Grand Designs
programme.desc: Kevin McCloud meets Rosa and her partner Craig who are turning a century-old, family-owned, decommissioned steam railway reservoir into a home. Their radical plan to reinvent the reservoir into a unique living space involves punching huge holes through the walls to allow light to flood in, a mezzanine with views across the valley and a concrete extension with four bedrooms. Along the way they encounter a pandemic, numerous money crises, pregnancy and a schedule that grows from 12 months to over three years, is it worth it for Rosa to have the reservoir home she has dreamt of since childhood?

programme.title: Britain's Most Expensive Houses
programme.desc: Sales broker John has a vast family home to sell in the stunning New Forest. Surrounded by a national park and with 26 acres of grounds, including a swimming pool, an orchard and private woodland, this 12-bedroom home built in 1897 has an asking price of 9million. Meanwhile, managing director Guy and Aoife work on one of their smallest properties - an industrial-style one-bedroom pied--terre in Pimlico in central London, which belongs to the chief executive of Brighton Football Club

programme.title: Two Men on a Bike
programme.desc: David Baddiel and Hugh Dennis travel along the Canal du Midi. Along the way, Hugh and David visit an artisanal dye expert who reveals the ancient magic behind turning things blue. At the Seuil de Naurouze, they gatecrash an unusual local fiesta, before dining in Castelnaudary - the cassoulet capital of the world. This leg of the journey culminates at the medieval citadel of Carcassonne

programme.title: Sandstorm (Bawandar)
programme.desc: Shoba T. Mathur works for the Central Government in India and her job is to create awareness against child-marriage and other social evils that prevail due to general misinterpretation of the Hindu Shastras that demean women, particularly in Dhabri, a village in the state of Rajasthan. She does succeed in recruiting a young housewife, Saanvri, the mother of a young girl, Kamli, and wife of rickshaw driver, Sohan. Saanvri goes around the village raising awareness, and incurs the wrath of the village elders, mostly members of the Gujjar family. When Saanvri persists with her efforts, five of the men severely beat-up Sohan, and gang-rape Saanvri. A devastated Saanvri and Sohan decide to get justice. They go to the Police Station, but the Police Inspector refuses to lodge a complaint until and unless he gets a Medical report. The doctor will not issue a medical report until and until he gets Court Order. Sohan and Saanvri, with Shobha's help do go through this process, and a complaint is finally lodged. Despite of this, the Gujjars are not arrested and continue to wander around, bragging about their experience with Saanvri. Saanvri's case then gets nation-wide attention, with the Prime Minister himself entrusting this investigation to the Central Bureau of Investigation. The Gujjars are arrested and tried in Court, but are fully aware that this is nothing but a charade, for they have the backing of the local Member of the Legislative Assembly, Dhanraj Meena, who has hired a lawyer, Purohit, and has instructed him to ensure that the Gujjars are not held liable. Watch as Judge after Judge is transferred, even the Prosecuting Attorney is of a upper caste, and is under pressure from the Gujjar community. Faced with a corrupt police force, an even more corrupt Judicial system fueled more by wealth, influence, and caste rather than the rule of law, will Saanvri succeed in getting the justice she deserves?

Asuntos familiares
programme.desc: Los hermanos Alice y Louis, que se han evitado durante ms de veinte aos, se ven obligados a reunirse despus de una tragedia.

programme.title: La biblioteca de los libros rechazados
programme.desc: Una editora descubre una novela magistral en una biblioteca que guarda obras rechazadas por las editoriales. El autor es Henry Pick, un cocinero ya fallecido que nunca haba tocado un libro.

programme.title: Bordertown - T2, E01: Five Finger Exercise, Part 1
programme.desc: Un doble asesinato desencadena una investigacin que lleva a Kari Sorjonen al otro lado de la frontera. Sorjonen se da cuenta de que algo del pasado ha regresado.

programme.title: Bordertown - T2, E02: Five Finger Exercise, Part 2
programme.desc: Sorjonen tiene que averiguar la verdad sobre el pasado de Lena para atrapar a un asesino que no tiene nada que perder.

programme.title: Bordertown - T2, E03: The Rite of Spring, Part 1
programme.desc: Un feto conservado en formol es encontrado en la casa de la directora de la guardera, Susanna Lehto. Las investigaciones de Sorjonen revelan una red de silencio relacionada con los nios.

programme.title: Bordertown - T2, E04: The Rite of Spring, Part 2
programme.desc: Despus de que el pasado de la directora de la guardera salga a la a la luz, Sorjonen es el nico que cree que an no se ha descubierto toda la verdad.

programme.title: Bordertown - T2, E05: Cat's Cradle, Part 1
programme.desc: Sorjonen pide una excedencia por el estado de salud de su mujer. A pleno da, un joven es tiroteado en el Castillo de Arena de Lappeenranta. Niko Uusitalo se convierte en el detective a cargo del caso.

programme.title: Grace de Mnaco
programme.desc: Grace Kelly, una gran estrella de Hollywood, renunci a su carrera como actriz para casarse en 1956 con el prncipe Rainiero III y convertirse en Su Alteza Serensima la Princesa Gracia de Mnaco.

programme.title: Grace de Mnaco
programme.desc: Grace Kelly, una gran estrella de Hollywood, renunci a su carrera como actriz para casarse en 1956 con el prncipe Rainiero III y convertirse en Su Alteza Serensima la Princesa Gracia de Mnaco.

programme.title: Hijos del sol
programme.desc: Al, un nio de 12 aos y sus tres amigos trabajan para sobrevivir y ayudar a sus familias haciendo pequeos trabajos en un garaje y cometiendo pequeos delitos para conseguir dinero rpido.

programme.title: My Stolen Planet
